OleDb_DataSource_Description:
Returns a table of SQL tables and views from the OLE DB data source specified by the connection string {0}. {0} can be text or a record of property value pairs. Property values can either be text or number. An optional record parameter, {1}, may be provided to specify additional properties. The record can contain the following fields:
    {1:type}
    The record parameter is specified as [option1 = value1, option2 = value2...] or [Query = "select ..."] for example.

